data.description: This craftsman-style home is nestled on a 1.03-acre wooded lot, offering a rustic and peaceful atmosphere. With 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a bonus room, this 1750 square foot home provides ample space for comfortable living. The interior boasts blown-in insulation, ensuring energy efficiency and lower utility bills. Enjoy outdoor living on the deck or front porch, perfect for relaxing or entertaining guests. Warm up next to the woodburning stove during colder months, and stay connected with 1 gig per second internet speed. A small creek adds to the serene ambiance of the property. This home also features underground utilities, a new driveway, a large carport, a new oven, and stunning quartz counters in the kitchen. Located just 2 minutes from Greers Ferry Lake, you'll have easy access to water activities and breathtaking views. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this stunning home in a tranquil setting. Be sure to click the video links for the 3D tour and drone footage! Agents more info in remarks and docs. Possibly eligible for a VA assumable loan.
